{"cells":[{"value":"#### OBJECTIVE 1: ENCOUNTERS OVERVIEW\n\n- a. How many total encounters occurred each year?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"/*\nCreate cte to \n1. counts encounters,\n2. create column encounter_year - \n    start year when both start and stop year are the sem\n    \"start to stop\" when start and stop years are not the same\n*/\nWITH encounter_period AS (\n    SELECT \n    count(*) as num_encounters,\n    CASE\n        -- line below extracts year component of the timestamp and compares it\n\n        WHEN extract(year from start) = extract(year from stop) THEN extract(year from start)::text\n        ELSE extract(year from start) || ' to ' || extract(year from stop)::text\n        END AS encounter_year\nFROM encounters0\nGROUP BY start, stop\n)\nSELECT \n    encounter_year, -- select encounter year created in the cte above\n    count(*) as num_encounter -- count number of year occurance\nFROM encounter_period\nGROUP BY encounter_year -- group by the year\nORDER BY num_encounter desc -- other by descending number of num_encounter\nLIMIT 10;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- b. For each year, what percentage of all encounters belonged to each encounter class\n-- (ambulatory, outpatient, wellness, urgent care, emergency, and inpatient)?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"/*\nGet encounterclass, how many times it occured, then percentage of the encounter class\nover all other encounterclass*/\nSELECT \n    encounterclass,\n    count(*) as occurence,\n    round(count(*) * 100.0 / sum(count(*)) over(), 2) as perc_occurence\nFROM encounters0\nGROUP BY encounterclass\nORDER BY occurence desc\nLIMIT 5;\n","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- c. What percentage of encounters were over 24 hours versus under 24 hours?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"/*\nstop - start converted to interval of hours\ncategorize them ad over 24 hours and under 24 hours as duration_group\n*/\nWITH duration_cte AS (\n    SELECT \n        CASE \n            WHEN stop - start > interval '24 hours' THEN 'Over 24 Hours'\n            ELSE 'Under 24 Hours'\n        END AS duration_group\n    FROM encounters0\n)\n/*\nselect duration group,\ncount number of occurance\nfind percentage of occurrence over\n*/\nSELECT \n    duration_group,\n    count(*) AS occurrence,\n    round(count(*) * 100.0 / sum(count(*)) over(), 2) AS percentage\nFROM duration_cte\nGROUP BY duration_group;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"-- OBJECTIVE 2: COST & COVERAGE INSIGHTS\n\n- a. How many encounters had zero payer coverage, and what percentage of total encounters does this represent?\n","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"select \ncase \n    when payer_coverage = 0.00 then 'Zero Coverage'\n    else 'Non-zero Coverage' end as zero_coverage,\n    count(*) as num,\n    round(count(*) * 100.0 / sum(count(*)) over(), 2) AS percentage\nfrom encounters0\ngroup by zero_coverage;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- b. What are the top 10 most frequent procedures performed and the average base cost for each?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"/*\nget top 10 most frequent procedures performed and their average base cost\n*/\nselect \n    p.description,\n    count(*) as num_procedures,\n    round(avg(base_cost) ,2) as avg_base_cost_usd -- average base cost in usd\nfrom procedures0 as p\nleft join encounters0 as e\non p.patient = e.id\nwhere right(p.description,11) = '(procedure)'\nGROUP BY p.description\norder by num_procedures desc\nlimit 10;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- c. What are the top 10 procedures with the highest average base cost and the number of times they were performed?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"/*\nGet top 10 higheest average base cost and number of of times they were performed\n*/\nselect \n    left(p.description,length(p.description) - length('(procedure)')) as procedure_name,\n    round(avg(base_cost) ,2) as avg_base_cost_usd, -- average base cost in usd\n    count(*) as num_perf_procedures\nfrom procedures0 as p\nleft join encounters0 as e\non p.patient = e.id\nwhere right(p.description,11) = '(procedure)'\nGROUP BY p.description\norder by avg_base_cost_usd desc\nlimit 10;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- d. What is the average total claim cost for encounters, broken down by payer?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"/*\nget average total claim from encounters\nbreak it down by payer\n*/\n\nselect \n    p.name,\n    round(avg(e.total_claim_cost), 2) as avg_total_claim_cost\nfrom encounters0 as e\ninner join payers0 as p\non e.payer = p.id\ngroup by p.name\norder by avg_total_claim_cost desc;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"### OBJECTIVE 3: PATIENT BEHAVIOR ANALYSIS\n\n- a. How many unique patients were admitted each quarter over time?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"SELECT \n    -- extract(year from start) as year,\n    extract(quarter from start) as quarter,\n    count(distinct patient) unique_patients\nFROM encounters0\nGROUP BY quarter\nORDER BY  quarter;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"select \n    count(distinct patient), -- p.id) unique_patients,\n    extract(quarter from e.start) as quarter\nfrom encounters0 as e\n-- inner join patients0 as p\n-- on p.id = e.patient\ngroup by quarter;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- b. How many patients were readmitted within 30 days of a previous encounter?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"- c. Which patients had the most readmissions?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"}],"metadata":{"custom":{"cells":[{"value":"#### OBJECTIVE 1: ENCOUNTERS OVERVIEW\n\n- a. How many total encounters occurred each year?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"/*\nCreate cte to \n1. counts encounters,\n2. create column encounter_year - \n    start year when both start and stop year are the sem\n    \"start to stop\" when start and stop years are not the same\n*/\nWITH encounter_period AS (\n    SELECT \n    count(*) as num_encounters,\n    CASE\n        -- line below extracts year component of the timestamp and compares it\n\n        WHEN extract(year from start) = extract(year from stop) THEN extract(year from start)::text\n        ELSE extract(year from start) || ' to ' || extract(year from stop)::text\n        END AS encounter_year\nFROM encounters0\nGROUP BY start, stop\n)\nSELECT \n    encounter_year, -- select encounter year created in the cte above\n    count(*) as num_encounter -- count number of year occurance\nFROM encounter_period\nGROUP BY encounter_year -- group by the year\nORDER BY num_encounter desc -- other by descending number of num_encounter\nLIMIT 10;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- b. For each year, what percentage of all encounters belonged to each encounter class\n-- (ambulatory, outpatient, wellness, urgent care, emergency, and inpatient)?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"/*\nGet encounterclass, how many times it occured, then percentage of the encounter class\nover all other encounterclass*/\nSELECT \n    encounterclass,\n    count(*) as occurence,\n    round(count(*) * 100.0 / sum(count(*)) over(), 2) as perc_occurence\nFROM encounters0\nGROUP BY encounterclass\nORDER BY occurence desc\nLIMIT 5;\n","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- c. What percentage of encounters were over 24 hours versus under 24 hours?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"/*\nstop - start converted to interval of hours\ncategorize them ad over 24 hours and under 24 hours as duration_group\n*/\nWITH duration_cte AS (\n    SELECT \n        CASE \n            WHEN stop - start > interval '24 hours' THEN 'Over 24 Hours'\n            ELSE 'Under 24 Hours'\n        END AS duration_group\n    FROM encounters0\n)\n/*\nselect duration group,\ncount number of occurance\nfind percentage of occurrence over\n*/\nSELECT \n    duration_group,\n    count(*) AS occurrence,\n    round(count(*) * 100.0 / sum(count(*)) over(), 2) AS percentage\nFROM duration_cte\nGROUP BY duration_group;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"-- OBJECTIVE 2: COST & COVERAGE INSIGHTS\n\n- a. How many encounters had zero payer coverage, and what percentage of total encounters does this represent?\n","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"select \ncase \n    when payer_coverage = 0.00 then 'Zero Coverage'\n    else 'Non-zero Coverage' end as zero_coverage,\n    count(*) as num,\n    round(count(*) * 100.0 / sum(count(*)) over(), 2) AS percentage\nfrom encounters0\ngroup by zero_coverage;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- b. What are the top 10 most frequent procedures performed and the average base cost for each?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"/*\nget top 10 most frequent procedures performed and their average base cost\n*/\nselect \n    p.description,\n    count(*) as num_procedures,\n    round(avg(base_cost) ,2) as avg_base_cost_usd -- average base cost in usd\nfrom procedures0 as p\nleft join encounters0 as e\non p.patient = e.id\nwhere right(p.description,11) = '(procedure)'\nGROUP BY p.description\norder by num_procedures desc\nlimit 10;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- c. What are the top 10 procedures with the highest average base cost and the number of times they were performed?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"/*\nGet top 10 higheest average base cost and number of of times they were performed\n*/\nselect \n    left(p.description,length(p.description) - length('(procedure)')) as procedure_name,\n    round(avg(base_cost) ,2) as avg_base_cost_usd, -- average base cost in usd\n    count(*) as num_perf_procedures\nfrom procedures0 as p\nleft join encounters0 as e\non p.patient = e.id\nwhere right(p.description,11) = '(procedure)'\nGROUP BY p.description\norder by avg_base_cost_usd desc\nlimit 10;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- d. What is the average total claim cost for encounters, broken down by payer?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"/*\nget average total claim from encounters\nbreak it down by payer\n*/\n\nselect \n    p.name,\n    round(avg(e.total_claim_cost), 2) as avg_total_claim_cost\nfrom encounters0 as e\ninner join payers0 as p\non e.payer = p.id\ngroup by p.name\norder by avg_total_claim_cost desc;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"### OBJECTIVE 3: PATIENT BEHAVIOR ANALYSIS\n\n- a. How many unique patients were admitted each quarter over time?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"SELECT \n    -- extract(year from start) as year,\n    extract(quarter from start) as quarter,\n    count(distinct patient) unique_patients\nFROM encounters0\nGROUP BY quarter\nORDER BY  quarter;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"select \n    count(distinct patient), -- p.id) unique_patients,\n    extract(quarter from e.start) as quarter\nfrom encounters0 as e\n-- inner join patients0 as p\n-- on p.id = e.patient\ngroup by quarter;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- b. How many patients were readmitted within 30 days of a previous encounter?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"- c. Which patients had the most readmissions?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"}],"metadata":{"custom":{"cells":[],"metadata":{"custom":{"cells":[{"value":"#### OBJECTIVE 1: ENCOUNTERS OVERVIEW\n\n- a. How many total encounters occurred each year?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"WITH encounter_period AS (\n    SELECT \n    count(*) as num_encounters,\n    CASE\n        WHEN extract(year from start) = extract(year from stop) THEN extract(year from start)::text\n        ELSE extract(year from start) || ' to ' || extract(year from stop)::text\n        END AS encounter_year\nFROM encounters0\nGROUP BY start, stop\n)\nSELECT \n    encounter_year,\n    count(*) as num_encounter\nFROM encounter_period\nGROUP BY encounter_year\nORDER BY num_encounter desc\nLIMIT 10;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- b. For each year, what percentage of all encounters belonged to each encounter class\n-- (ambulatory, outpatient, wellness, urgent care, emergency, and inpatient)?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"SELECT \n    encounterclass,\n    count(*) as occurence,\n    round(count(*) * 100.0 / sum(count(*)) over(), 2) as perc_occurence\nFROM encounters0\nGROUP BY encounterclass\nORDER BY occurence desc\nLIMIT 5;\n","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- c. What percentage of encounters were over 24 hours versus under 24 hours?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"WITH duration_cte AS (\n    SELECT \n        CASE \n            WHEN stop - start > interval '24 hours' THEN 'Over 24 Hours'\n            ELSE 'Under 24 Hours'\n        END AS duration_group\n    FROM encounters0\n)\nSELECT \n    duration_group,\n    count(*) AS occurrence,\n    round(count(*) * 100.0 / sum(count(*)) over(), 2) AS percentage\nFROM duration_cte\nGROUP BY duration_group;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"-- OBJECTIVE 2: COST & COVERAGE INSIGHTS\n\n- a. How many encounters had zero payer coverage, and what percentage of total encounters does this represent?\n","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"-- SELECT p.name, e.description\n-- FROM encounters0 as e\n-- LEFT JOIN payers0 as p \n-- ON p.id = e.payer\n-- LIMIT 10;\n\nSELECT\n    *\n    -- ,\n    -- CASE\n    --     WHEN name = 'NO_INSURANCE' THEN 0\n    --     ELSE 1\n    --     END AS num_payer\nFROM payers0\nLIMIT 100;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- b. What are the top 10 most frequent procedures performed and the average base cost for each?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"- c. What are the top 10 procedures with the highest average base cost and the number of times they were performed?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"- d. What is the average total claim cost for encounters, broken down by payer?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"-- Write your SQL query here\nSELECT NOW();","kind":"sql","language":"sql"}],"metadata":{"custom":{"cells":[],"metadata":{"custom":{"cells":[{"value":"#### OBJECTIVE 1: ENCOUNTERS OVERVIEW\n\n- a. How many total encounters occurred each year?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"WITH encounter_period AS (\n    SELECT \n    count(*) as num_encounters,\n    CASE\n        WHEN extract(year from start) = extract(year from stop) THEN extract(year from start)::text\n        ELSE extract(year from start) || ' to ' || extract(year from stop)::text\n        END AS encounter_year\nFROM encounters0\nGROUP BY start, stop\n)\nSELECT \n    encounter_year,\n    count(*) as num_encounter\nFROM encounter_period\nGROUP BY encounter_year\nORDER BY num_encounter desc\nLIMIT 10;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- b. For each year, what percentage of all encounters belonged to each encounter class\n-- (ambulatory, outpatient, wellness, urgent care, emergency, and inpatient)?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"SELECT \n    encounterclass,\n    count(*) as occurence,\n    round(count(*) * 100.0 / sum(count(*)) over(), 2) as perc_occurence\nFROM encounters0\nGROUP BY encounterclass\nORDER BY occurence desc\nLIMIT 5;\n","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"- c. What percentage of encounters were over 24 hours versus under 24 hours?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"WITH duration_cte AS (\n    SELECT \n        CASE \n            WHEN stop - start > interval '24 hours' THEN 'Over 24 Hours'\n            ELSE 'Under 24 Hours'\n        END AS duration_group\n    FROM encounters0\n)\nSELECT \n    duration_group,\n    count(*) AS occurrence,\n    round(count(*) * 100.0 / sum(count(*)) over(), 2) AS percentage\nFROM duration_cte\nGROUP BY duration_group;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"-- OBJECTIVE 2: COST & COVERAGE INSIGHTS\n\n-- a. How many encounters had zero payer coverage, and what percentage of total encounters does this represent?\n\n-- b. What are the top 10 most frequent procedures performed and the average base cost for each?\n\n-- c. What are the top 10 procedures with the highest average base cost and the number of times they were performed?\n\n-- d. What is the average total claim cost for encounters, broken down by payer?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"-- Write your SQL query here\nSELECT NOW();","kind":"sql","language":"sql"}],"metadata":{"custom":{"cells":[],"metadata":{"custom":{"cells":[{"value":"#### OBJECTIVE 1: ENCOUNTERS OVERVIEW\n\n- a. How many total encounters occurred each year?\n\n- b. For each year, what percentage of all encounters belonged to each encounter class\n-- (ambulatory, outpatient, wellness, urgent care, emergency, and inpatient)?\n\n- c. What percentage of encounters were over 24 hours versus under 24 hours?\n\n","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"WITH encounter_period AS (\n    SELECT \n    count(*) as num_encounters,\n    CASE\n        WHEN extract(year from start) = extract(year from stop) THEN extract(year from start)::text\n        ELSE extract(year from start) || ' to ' || extract(year from stop)::text\n        END AS encounter_year\nFROM encounters\nGROUP BY start, stop\n)\nSELECT \n    encounter_year,\n    count(*) as num_encounter\nFROM encounter_period\nGROUP BY encounter_year\nORDER BY num_encounter desc\nLIMIT 10;","kind":"sql","language":"sql"},{"value":"-- OBJECTIVE 2: COST & COVERAGE INSIGHTS\n\n-- a. How many encounters had zero payer coverage, and what percentage of total encounters does this represent?\n\n-- b. What are the top 10 most frequent procedures performed and the average base cost for each?\n\n-- c. What are the top 10 procedures with the highest average base cost and the number of times they were performed?\n\n-- d. What is the average total claim cost for encounters, broken down by payer?","kind":"markdown","language":"markdown"},{"value":"-- Write your SQL query here\nSELECT NOW();","kind":"sql","language":"sql"}],"metadata":{"enableScripts":true}},"enableScripts":true}},"connectionId":"1772718987289","databaseName":"hospital","host":"localhost","port":5432,"username":"njoku","enableScripts":true}},"connectionId":"1772718987289","databaseName":"hospital","host":"localhost","port":5432,"username":"njoku","enableScripts":true}},"connectionId":"1772718987289","databaseName":"hospital","host":"localhost","port":5432,"username":"njoku","enableScripts":true}},"connectionId":"1772718987289","databaseName":"hospital","host":"localhost","port":5432,"username":"njoku","enableScripts":true}},"connectionId":"1772718987289","databaseName":"hospital","host":"localhost","port":5432,"username":"njoku","enableScripts":true}},"connectionId":"1772718987289","databaseName":"hospital","host":"localhost","port":5432,"username":"njoku"}}